* Iron Raptor dodged the shots from Sinesis and turned towards Liono, she 
had just got here and now she was being ordered to leave?
She sighed and looked back at Plintissa, she put her gun away and hopped 
into the speeder. It was only seconds before the engine roared
and the bike hovered above the ground, Iron Raptor looked at Plintissa 
again.*

" Hop on, we're ordered to get out of here!"
